fields.description:
1) Download the app "Raiwei tickets" on your smartphone; 
2) Register in the application "Raiwei tickets"; 
3) Fill in the fields in choosing a ticket in the vertical position of the smartphone; 
4) Select the current ticket;
 5) Turn the phone to a horizontal position; 
6) The application will give an error - "You do not have actual tickets."
 7) Actual result: in the horizontal position the application "Raiwei tickets" does not work.

шаги воспроизведения:
 * открыть [http://www.nibulon.com/data/zakupivlya-silgospprodukcii/kalkulyator-znizhok.html ;|http://www.nibulon.com/data/zakupivlya-silgospprodukcii/kalkulyator-znizhok.html]
 * заполнить поля буквами;
 * нажать кнопку рассчитать; 

ожидаемый результат:

вывод сообщения об ошибки - только числа разрешены;

фактический результат: нули в расчете;

1. Download and install from the AppStore application from "Ukrazaliznytsi";

2. Allow Auto-rotate screen on device;

3. Enter the direction "From" and "Where" and select values ​​from the drop-down list of dates and times;

4. Click on the "Search for trains".

5. Flip the device to a horizontal position.

Expected result: Relocation of routes on the screen from vertical to horizontal position.

Actual result: The location of the routes on the screen remains upright after turning the device to a horizontal position.
